long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: In this game, you are given some figures of some super cars and the picture is cut in many small parts. You are also given a layout of the cut parts. You just need to put the right piece in the right place so it could be a complete image in the same manner.
